dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Caliente Mountain quadrangle, San Luis Obispo & Santa Barbara counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle CALIENTE MOUNTAIN, CA 1959, AMS2054 III SE -- Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
